<h2>Persistant Configuration events.</h2>

These events are used deliver persistant configuration to the webbrick gateway and to update the 
persistaant configuration. The advantages of delivering persistant configuration using the event delivery mechanism
are:
<ol>
<li>Information can be stored in multiple places for redundancy.</li>
<li>The choice of storage can be chosen to suit the implementation, local disk, remote server.</li>
<li>We have a single persistent data store.</li>
<li>The data store could be partioned and distributed.</li>
</ol>

